ation factor degrades by at most O(log(min{n, h})). This is an\nimprovement over previously-known constructions with inflation factor O(log n).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 May 2013 23:51:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-05-06"}
