on\" of\nPioneer probes. All is obtained without any change in theories of standard\nspectroscopy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 3 May 2013 08:25:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 9 Jun 2013 19:29:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-15"}
